<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Products üõí</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a1c4fd, #c2e9fb);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .container {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 40px;
      max-width: 1100px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.8em;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      color: #ffeb3b;
    }

    .products {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 25px;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      border-radius: 14px;
      width: 280px;
      padding: 25px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      text-align: left;
      transition: transform 0.3s, background 0.3s;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
    }

    .card h2 {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 1.5em;
      color: #ffe082;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 1em;
      color: #f5f5f5;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 35px;
      text-decoration: none;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745, #85d37d);
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 28px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.1em;
      transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.3s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #218838, #28a745);
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* Animation */
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Our Products ü•¶üçé</h1>

    <div class="products">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Fresh Apples üçé</h2>
        <p>Sweet, crunchy, and packed with nutrients. Perfect for a healthy snack!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Organic Carrots ü•ï</h2>
        <p>Locally grown and full of flavor. Great for soups and salads.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Green Spinach üåø</h2>
        <p>Rich in iron and vitamins. A great choice for smoothies and meals.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/contact" class="btn">üìû Contact Us</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
